description: Generates, QA-reviews, and maintains a library of reusable support macros from real ticket clusters — so every rep pulls a reviewed, on-brand reply instead of writing from scratch. Keep Zendesk macros or Intercom snippets. Replace the outdated canned responses, the Google Doc nobody updates, and the tone drift nobody catches.
